0103.name: Unknown
0103.message:
There is a problem with the system memory.

For help, make a note of the error code and visit
support.nintendo.com
0103.short_solution:
Usually happens on 32GB Wii U models having a Hynix chip,
this chip has a problem that slowly corrupts its data overtime,
there is nothing much to do except backing up the MLC
and replacing the Hynix chip entierly.
